# {{context|chemistry}} A glass flask used in a [[laboratory]] for holding chemical liquids and solutions. They are similar in shape to a [[Florence flask]], but with a longer neck and wider flat bottom. The neck is marked so that a particular volume of liquid can be measured with high [[precision]].

